Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.59,0:00:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星好漂亮喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.22,0:00:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.51,0:00:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德, 今天真是谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.06,0:00:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.07,0:00:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捡垃圾这点小事随时可以找我帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.42,0:00:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实不是单纯来捡垃圾的就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.86,0:00:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们来这个地方做什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.26,0:00:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然擅自乱捡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.72,0:00:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底要干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.86,0:00:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这把圣剑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.16,0:00:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说没有强大的魔力\N就绝对无法拔起来对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说把它弄到手的人将能称霸世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.70,0:00:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我想应该只是把破铜烂铁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但因为没人能拔得起它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.24,0:00:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果就被爱钱的村长\N拿来当成赚钱的道具了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拔起来了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.65,0:00:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.63,0:00:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"圣剑之森露营场"\N"圣剑之森高尔夫球场"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"圣剑之森美术馆"\N还有公园跟旅馆…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我远大的圣剑计划啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:01:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下爽快多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.52,0:01:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么, 这把剑该怎么处理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.38,0:01:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们说不定会准备冒牌货代替
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.74,0:01:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得尽快将剑拔出来的事公诸于世才行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.90,0:01:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.31,0:01:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就拜托你啰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(比方说, 这是将杂志上号称无往不利的\N搭讪台词信以为真般的大胆邀请方式)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.85,0:03:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演习课上的好开心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.83,0:03:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是罗伊德大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过下一堂是魔法讲座
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.90,0:03:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能一边休息一边上…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家注意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.11,0:03:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讲座课程取消了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.67,0:03:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天起要改为实际演练课程
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.86,0:03:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选出和六条魔法学园进行交流比赛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.08,0:03:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交流比赛?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是每年都会举行的学校活动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.58,0:03:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过最近这几年好像都是亚萨米输就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.59,0:03:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年我们绝对会赢, 绝对会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细听好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.92,0:03:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法的使用方法大致可分成三种类
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诵念咒语的"咏唱"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刻划图案或文本的"纹章"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.88,0:03:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运用魔石或魔杖的"媒介"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为每种方法都有其优缺点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.65,0:03:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据状况随机应变是最好的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(对魔法假人)\N赶快开始做练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧殆尽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧殆尽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个表现得都很不错喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.83,0:04:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.25,0:04:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男骚带劲吧, 我艳!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.44,0:04:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃螺丝了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样叫失败?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.73,0:04:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好, 你就参加风魔法的比赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想也知道不行啊, 会出人命的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么, 明明还有保持原型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉, 罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来还是不能让你出赛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.33,0:04:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想学习回复魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校很擅长使用回复魔法对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.13,0:04:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样没错, 但你为什么要学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要为重要的人疗伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.15,0:04:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加深彼此的牵绊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后把生米煮成熟饭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.47,0:05:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回复魔法可是最不好学的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多人抱着半吊子的觉悟接触\N后来都学得很挫折
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有很多搞错使用方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.77,0:05:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,误将小石子或泥土混入导致伤口化脓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后不得不动手术摘除的案例喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到莉荷这么清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.32,0:05:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然很困难\N那不就更应该趁现在学起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该也有助于提升基础魔力才对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是, 我也想学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要来举办科林式回复新训营呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.28,0:05:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说我们需要伤患
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀, 这里竟然有个\N除了耐打以外一无是处的男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.22,0:05:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好, 赛莲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜利总是得伴随着牺牲的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.63,0:05:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧, 马上就能治好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管接下来被痛扁多少次都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.93,0:06:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(紧盯)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪位啊!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是吓到你了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们姑且算是客人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.90,0:06:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人? 看起来不太像啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.94,0:06:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是梅娜·希农
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我的妹妹费萝·希农
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是六条的佣兵姊妹?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们目前就在那个六条当学生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这几位学生有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.58,0:06:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在找这女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在抓苍蝇对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍蝇?\N(注: 日文音近"是")
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思, 都怪我刚刚没有避开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好进门的人是罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人不是莉荷小姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的, 我们就读同一所士官学校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收我为徒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.10,0:07:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是料理, 洗衣或开路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都愿意做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必收我为徒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…这里是玛丽小姐的家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.92,0:07:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能自行决定…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要住在这里, 我叫费萝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.96,0:07:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说"是"了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么事不宜迟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.55,0:07:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我立刻为你刷背
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问浴室在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒盐, 快撒盐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了, 罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的肋骨断了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快点做治疗才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点小事不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.28,0:08:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骨折花三小时就能治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.73,0:08:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了, 得赶快做晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就去准备, 玛丽小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.54,0:08:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续在意这些也不是办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.50,0:08:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得习惯罗伊德的能力才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.30,0:08:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟短期内都会和他住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话希望能永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.53,0:08:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你和罗伊德来了一场\N当日往返的圣剑村之旅?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我们是去工作啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.45,0:08:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你玩得很开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.17,0:08:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德的笑容都尽收眼底了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.09,0:08:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然丢下我顾着自己享乐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管她我们先吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.12,0:08:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是吃什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个萝莉老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:09:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然冷不防地把我变成蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好, 今天也要卯足干劲练习喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交流比赛的日子快到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看他们这么卖力\N还是先准备一些奖品好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么这么想赢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌的那个蛇女成为了六条的校长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.17,0:09:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇女?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指的是我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.78,0:09:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝露
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌, 瞧你那副表情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们明明这么久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来做什么的, 比赛还没开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找你找好久了, 莉荷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:10:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴看到你过得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那只秘银的义肢也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝露·卡希菲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我还在六条时的同年级生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.76,0:10:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是个为了成为第一名\N巴结老师逼走了好几个竞争对手的讨厌鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后还爬上校长的位子了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉荷, 你快点回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不想再失去更重要的东西的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想对过去培育自己的地方做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去是过去, 重要的是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就等交流比赛那天再听你的答复吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.23,0:10:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.05,0:10:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会等待你的答复的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.24,0:10:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费萝, 该走啰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:10:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说罗伊德大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:11:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您和那女人发生过什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.25,0:11:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过她好像说想和我住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情到底为什么变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.15,0:11:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今…今天的晚餐看起来也很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好尴尬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.41,0:11:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久之前才被他看到我那副模样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个, 玛丽小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.76,0:11:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要去鼓励一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不晓得该为那个人做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难…难道说他想为我打气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.18,0:11:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是女孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德好温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.96,0:11:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是比较保险的方法\N不过邀她去喝茶怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.98,0:12:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错, 简单来说就是约会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.36,0:12:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.13,0:12:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我这种软弱又不起眼的男人邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的会高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她当然会很高兴啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强硬点也没关系, 牵住她的手提出邀约吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是我的…不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是女孩子的憧憬喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.58,0:12:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的建议
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.40,0:12:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我明天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.78,0:12:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去邀莉荷小姐约会看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉荷小姐再不快点恢复正常的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德大人根本就不会注意我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉荷小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我珍藏的罗伊德大人的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见这张照片你应该就打起精神了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:12:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉荷是一路从严酷的世界走来的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在应该讲个黄色笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易快痊愈的伤口…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉荷小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啊, 这次换罗伊德吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请和我一起去约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喜欢甜甜圈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.68,0:13:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉荷小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以请你告诉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问莉荷小姐到底发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这问题一定让你难以启齿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我很担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉荷小姐在那天之后就一直很没有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.61,0:13:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.49,0:13:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人的气氛竟然这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟑螂…?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对, 是赛莲!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你, 莉荷小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:13:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是为了这个才…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:13:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在孤儿院长大的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在那里遇见了萝露
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.13,0:14:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝露拥有魔法的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而她也教了我许多魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我因为左手的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法帮上孤儿院任何忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来某一天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝露回来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.96,0:14:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着秘银制的义肢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心想这样自己也能为孤儿院赚钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一来就能和萝露一起工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我却逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝露之所以会给我义肢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了通过秘银的力量增幅魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我以生命作为交换拔出"圣剑"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.33,0:14:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:14:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别直接用手碰它喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.11,0:15:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是触碰到魔力就会被吸走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你的义肢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它就像生了根的植物一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也在吸收着我的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法将它拆下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.42,0:15:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也只能一直不断逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管那家伙捏造了多少罪名\N设法通缉捉拿我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单讲就是要我去死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我过去最憧憬的大姊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不会再相信任何人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.67,0:15:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过别碰了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.69,0:15:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我现在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还只是因为人家可怜我\N才得以入学的士官候补生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.13,0:15:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会成为一个有出息的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.53,0:15:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请你相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.43,0:15:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会背叛莉荷小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个背叛者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.67,0:15:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候在这的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉荷小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.03,0:16:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不早点把那个义肢的事说出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在担心我?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然被人以莫须有的罪名通缉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我最近也被人不实指控说是跟踪狂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常能理解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别拿我和你相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.91,0:16:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.21,0:16:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你不在的话学园生活会变得很无趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们这次就在交流比赛中\N将对方吓得目瞪口呆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错, 我也会为你们加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.44,0:16:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的, 你们两个搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.29,0:16:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这主意还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.54,0:16:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加今天的示范赛的选手决定好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前只决定了这两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想请你今天当我的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.72,0:16:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不, 罗伊德他, 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.02,0:16:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你好像很困扰呢, 科林上校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.08,0:16:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音是从哪里传来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:16:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.87,0:17:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是无人不知无人不晓的\N那个有名的二年级首席
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.18,0:17:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米可娜·佐尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.74,0:17:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这群嚣张的半调子先让到一边去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.92,0:17:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来出场比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.65,0:17:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替这个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德·贝多那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.95,0:17:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接下来会让你了解到\N我比你还优秀的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会难得, 就拜托你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习赛现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.59,0:17:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好惊人的气势
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是魔石?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是媒介魔法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.64,0:17:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费萝是格斗家所以会使用道具作战喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.06,0:17:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.87,0:17:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.92,0:18:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秒杀?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜…胜负已分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.05,0:18:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.43,0:18:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我立刻为你治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连这种时候都还要瞧不起我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.90,0:18:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真亏你有脸摆出这种态度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.97,0:18:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明凭你一个人什么也办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米可娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好你没有伤得很重
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来, 包扎好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.33,0:18:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢谢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.06,0:18:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来我们好久不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:18:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明以前几乎每天都会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.56,0:19:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近都比较没有受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.02,0:19:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝杯咖啡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.36,0:19:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来, 黑咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米可娜喜欢的口味和我一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽小姐…玛丽小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.08,0:19:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米可娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.69,0:19:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是发烧了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.38,0:19:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发烧了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.04,0:19:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我多心了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.70,0:19:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能感觉到吐息的梦寐以求的超近距离!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能活在世上真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.68,0:19:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了, 玛丽小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米可娜学姊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.53,0:19:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在交流比赛的练习中见过面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.52,0:19:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交流比赛?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都到这个时候了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.65,0:19:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.38,0:19:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不说这个了, 先去做饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的, 我立刻去准备
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.01,0:19:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了, 我肚子都快饿扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:19:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的菜色是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在完成之前请先好好期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是罗伊德做的料理我什么都喜欢喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过前菜我想先吃凉拌番茄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.59,0:20:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能喝太多酒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.81,0:20:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将进行亚萨米士官学校\N对六条魔法学园的交流比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.48,0:20:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你决定好答复了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.86,0:20:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实就算会死我也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能帮上孤儿院和你的忙的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那只限于对过去的萝露·卡希菲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你只是个贪得无厌的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.69,0:20:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一条脱皮过了头的可悲的蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.25,0:20:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的老家会怎么样我可不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.61,0:20:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤儿院由我来守护
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.26,0:20:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天一定要让你吓到大喊"喔诶"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.16,0:21:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的"喔诶"\N我现在就原封不动的还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.87,0:21:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛开始之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.43,0:21:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此先发表奖赏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获胜者将能获得奖金
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.18,0:21:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及传说中的圣剑做为奖励
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔诶!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.99,0:22:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.78,0:22:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会和那个男人…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.13,0:23:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.66,0:23:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨好像会越下越大喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.85,0:23:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不嫌弃我可以陪你聊聊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.19,0:23:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算会讲得很久也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.57,0:23:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些不愿被人问起的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.49,0:23:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就让雨水将它们冲走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.57,0:23:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.19,0:23:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被抢走了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.03,0:23:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(比方说, 这是觉得一定会赢的人获胜了\N觉得一定会输的人也获胜了的交流比赛的开始)\N